<HL>
   Continental Airlines Holdings' Creditors
   Seek to Sue Former Chairman Lorenzo
   ----
   By Bridget O'Brian
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
02/13/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A4
</SO>
<CO>
   CTA K.SAI LABOR
</CO>
<MS>
CONSUMER CYCLICAL (CYC)
</MS>
